Package com.epam.training.dao.mysqldao

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MySQLBuildDAO
    Class MySQLBuildDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Builds of the Projects found in the application, and add new Builds.
    MySQLFeatureDAO
    Abstract class MySQLFeatureDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about abstract Features of Issues reported, add new Features and update them.
    MySQLIssueDAO
    Class MySQLIssueDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Issues reported in the application, add new Issues, update existent Issues, and delete them.
    MySQLMemberDAO
    Class MySQLMemberDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Members registered in the application, add and update data their data.
    MySQLPriorityDAO
    Class MySQLPriorityDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Priorities of Issues reported, add new and update existent Priorities.
    MySQLProjectDAO
    Class MySQLProjectDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Projects found in the application, add and update data their data.
    MySQLResolutionDAO
    Class MySQLResolutionDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Resolution of Issues reported, add new and update existent Resolutions.
    MySQLStatusDAO
    Class MySQLStatusDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Statuses of Issues reported and update existent Statuses.
    MySQLTypeDAO
    Class MySQLTypeDAO contains methods allowing to extract information about Types of Issues reported, add new and update existent Types.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MySQLFeatureDAO.FeatureField
    Enum FeatureField contains the list of the keys that are used to retrieve query and field constants from a Map.
